<!--pages/details/details.wxml-->
<view class='page'>
  <view class='page-img'>
    <image src='/images/{{gtlist.gimg}}'></image>
  </view>
  <view class='page-content'>
    <view class='title'>
      <image src='/images/tuijian.png'></image>
      <view class='name'>{{gtlist.gname}}</view>
      <view class='content'>{{gtlist.gcontent}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class='sale'>月销552份 | 好评率100%</view>
    <view class='price'>￥{{gtlist.gprice}}<text class='oldPrice'>￥{{oldPrice}}</text><text class='discount'>7.7折</text></view>
    <!-- <view class='time'>{{gtlist.gtime}}</view> -->
    <view class='desc'>
    <text>健康功效\n</text>
      香菜:增强免疫力、抗氧化、抗癌防癌 
      青椒:增强免疫力、抗氧化、抗癌防癌
      红椒:开胃、消食
    </view>
    <view class='step'>
      <text>做法：\n</text>
      1.准备食材。牛肉、干辣椒、青椒、姜蒜、葱  
      2.姜蒜切丝，干辣椒、小葱切段，青椒切圈  
      3.牛肉切片，放入淀粉、酱油，抓匀腌制入味  
      4.锅中加油烧热，放入姜蒜丝炒香  
      5.放入牛肉，稍稍有点变色了加白酒  
      6.放入干辣椒、青椒圈。加入孜然粉、鸡精调味  
      7.起锅前放入葱花即可
    </view>
  </view>

</view>
